      "text": "social ranking solutionの話",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b57a",
      "text": "from [2026/04/28]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b57b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704906
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b57c",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b57d",
      "text": " 今日はオンラインじゅぎょう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b57e",
      "text": "　[社会的選択理論]やってる人だった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b57f",
      "text": "　[social ranking solution]の話",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b580",
      "text": "　 あるメンバーの全ての組み合わせを、チームパフォーマンス順に並べたとき、ここからどのメンバーが一番優秀かを選ぶ方法を調べる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b581",
      "text": "　投票とは違うかな？と思ったのだが、[Plurality]という単語が出てきて驚いた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b582",
      "text": "  https://doi.org/10.1007/s10726-025-09957-6",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b583",
      "text": "  [plurality voting], [相対多数]のことみたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b584",
      "text": "   https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/相対多数_(投票)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b585",
      "text": " どうやら構造は同じらしい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b586",
      "text": "  [社会的選択理論]は、どの案を選択するかの投票ルールを調べる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b587",
      "text": "  これは[SRS理論]と似た箇所がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b588",
      "text": " 　Numeri 2015にて、投票ルールの決め方を決める構造が[SRS理論]に似ていると指摘",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b589",
      "text": " 　これを数学的に基礎づけたのが [Ranking Alternatives from Opinions on Criteria | Group Decision and Negotiation | Springer Nature Link https://doi.org/10.1007/s10726-025-09957-6]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    },
    {
      "id": "69f59fbf000000000021b58a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777704895,
      "updated": 1777704895
    }
  ]
}